c14ab151d5ed0e5e8","tid":267254,"uid":111669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己睇實d, 唔好亂發佢脾氣，到時比機會人有位入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係呢排關係嘛嘛先驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a65634d13427660068b347d4d05f5f64d2fcfd7","tid":267254,"uid":111669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇個條仔咩人<br />\n如果係狗公其實都幾易出事<br />\n睇你條女玩夠未幾大個<br />\n如果係25以下好大機會帽你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己觀察下蛛絲馬跡啦巴打<br />\n過來人上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉 所以我都好驚  我叫女朋友有啲介心 但佢似乎唔係好理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ec49065e2a77bddd7caad83a5179ab0c05a164","tid":267254,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母<br />\n同事都唔俾有係咪痴撚線架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係話同事都唔比有啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我唔識嗰個男仔 我緊係有戒心架  始終日對夜對難免會有感情架 就算我女朋友好自律 都唔代表人地唔狗公 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n萬一我地一嘈交 佢絕對方便乘人之危架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正正常常一間公司有好多同事我又冇所謂啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男仔始終係單獨環境係會大膽好多，加上女朋友冇乜介心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我擔心好正常姐？</span></blockquote><br />\n咁你同你女朋友講<br />\n同我地講把撚咩"},{"pid":"4199759523c7f8e5bdc9e674323526daf007db35","tid":267254,"uid":